msg: A patch from Ankit for "Error on Shopping List Page" Jain https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-4957
In the groovy EditShoppingList.groovy the value of lowIndex is 0 that's why in the ftl we should use lowIndex instead of lowIndex-1.
